('438','Billy Collins','1941-03-22T00:00:00.000000',null,'https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1385150456p7/438.jpg','William A. (\"Billy\") Collins is an American poet. He served two terms as the Poet Laureate of the United States from 2001 to 2003. In his home state, Collins has been recognized as a Literary Lion of the New York Public Library (1992) and selected as the New York State Poet for 2004.','New York City','United States'),
