  <a href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/31181.Breathing_Lessons\" title=\"Breathing Lessons\" rel=\"nofollow\">Breathing Lessons</a>
</i>, was awarded the Pulitzer Prize in 1988. She is a member of the American Academy of Arts and Letters.','Minneapolis, Minnesota','United States'),
